            x86_64-pc-linux-gnu-gcc -DHAVE_CONFIG_H -DNO_XMALLOC -I. -I/var/tmp/portage/dev-libs/libunistring-1.2/work/libunistring-1.2/lib -I..  -I. -I/var/tmp/portage/dev-libs/libunistring-1.2/work/libunistring-1.2/lib -I.. -I/var/tmp/portage/dev-libs/libunistring-1.2/work/libunistring-1.2 -DIN_LIBUNISTRING -DDEPENDS_ON_LIBICONV=1   -O3 -march=native -mtune=native -fomit-frame-pointer -pipe -c $sf || { rm -f config.h; exit 1; }; \
            sh ./exported.sh $of 1>&5; \
            rm -f $of `echo "$of" | sed -e 's,\\.o$,.lo,'`; \
            ;; \
        esac; \
      done; \
    } 5>&1 1>&2 \
      | sed -e 's,.* ,,' | grep -v '@' | LC_ALL=C sort | LC_ALL=C uniq \
      | LC_ALL=C /var/tmp/portage/dev-libs/libunistring-1.2/work/libunistring-1.2/build-aux/join-v-1 - /var/tmp/portage/dev-libs/libunistring-1.2/work/libunistring-1.2/lib/libunistring.sym \

  } 6>&1 && \

  fi \
fi
